BA personal guaranty + acquired entity multi-source complexity, Stairway brings B3-3.1-01 + B3-3.4-02 + Form 1084 acquired entity analysis + SBA personal guaranty DTI integration + lifecycle continuity narrative craft to produce clean qualifying.</strong></p>
